*VT100*utf8Fonts.font5: -*-terminus-medium-*-*-*-18-*-*-*-*-*-iso10646-1
*VT100*utf8Fonts.font6: -*-terminus-medium-*-*-*-20-*-*-*-*-*-iso10646-1

*VT100*faceName: \
xft:FantasqueSansMono Nerd Font Mono:style=Regular, \
xft:SauceCodePro Nerd Font Mono:style=Regular, \
xft:Monofur Nerd Font Mono:style=Regular

*VT100*faceSize : 17
*VT100*faceSize1: 14
